" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>演出结束后，Ficek <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/babyshambles-tease-more-reunion-shows-wait-for-it-3789330">暗示乐队可以正确团聚</a>。 “ 5分中的4个还不错……。等待……。”他写道。</p><p>多尔蒂（Doherty）后来发表了说：“这在卡片上，” <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/pete-doherty-interview-libertines-babyshambles-solo-new-music-future-2025-3823748">他告诉<i>NME</i></a> 。 “我们将重新聚在一起，与乐器一起播放一个旧歌，然后上台并做到这一点。但是，这是“谁”和“何时”，需要解决。我认为我们只是将那首歌保持在地平线上，并在明年处理那个。”</p><p>当被问及他是否想制作另一张Babyshambles的唱片时，他回答：“我不知道。前几天我写了一首新歌，我认为这确实是一首混乱的歌。谁知道？现在还有很长的路。</p><p>麦康奈尔（McConnell）在过去的十年中与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）</a>一起参加了他的巡回乐队。 Ficek并不是Babyshambles的第一位鼓手，但在2008年出发之前播放了前两张专辑。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pete-doherty-reunite-with-babyshambles-bandmates-to-perform-albion-and-fuck-forever-3848766">观看皮特·多赫蒂（Pete Doherty）与巴贝汉姆斯（Babyshambles）的队友团聚，表演“阿尔比恩（Albion）”和“他妈的永远”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
在Tiny Brighton复出演出中观看Wet Leet首次亮相的七首新歌https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-watch-wet-wet-leg-debut-seven-new-new-new-songs-at-tiny-brighton-comeback-gig-gig-3848756?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = watch-wet-leg-debut-seven-seven-seven-new-new-songs-at tiny-brighton-comeback-gook-gigPoppy Burton Mon, 24 Mar 2025 14:34:06 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3848756 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="湿腿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们将在今晚首都的蛾俱乐部（3月24日）的乌玛·瑟曼（Uma Thurman）别名下玩耍</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-wet-leg-debut-seven-new-songs-at-tiny-brighton-comeback-gig-3848756">邮政湿腿在Tiny Brighton复出演出中首次出现了七首新歌曲，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="湿腿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-wet-leg-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Wet-Leg">湿腿</a>昨天在他们亲密的布莱顿复出演出中首次亮相七首新歌 - 在下面观看镜头。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/wet-leg-cover-interview-2022-debut-album-chaise-longue-3184909"><em>NME</em> Big Read  - 湿腿：“我认为如果您玩得开心，音乐的真实性更大”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在周末，怀特岛乐队在周日（3月23日）和今晚（3月24日）在首都的蛾俱乐部（3月24日）在布莱顿的绿色门店戏弄了一场惊喜演出。</p><p>尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wet-leg-tease-two-uk-concerts-under-the-pseudonym-uma-thurman-3848538">最初宣布没有透露乐队的身份并以化名乌玛·瑟曼（Uma Thurman）共享</a>- 警告是真正的演员“不会出席”，但他们通过在其社交媒体帐户上分享了指向蛾俱乐部的链接来证实他们的参与。</p><p>今晚在蛾俱乐部演出的演出目前有一个等待名单，您可以<a href="https://dice.fm/event/yo9bex-uma-thurman-24th-mar-moth-club-london-tickets?sharer_id=67069e01137b5c0001f92939&amp;_branch_match_id=1182581233880617127&amp;utm_source=dice&amp;utm_campaign=event_share&amp;utm_medium=event_share&amp;_branch_referrer=H4sIAAAAAAAAAwXBvQ5AMBQG0Lcx6i1BKhEJg8FmEZMot9r4zVeJzbM7xz7P7XMhdndu4eJmDs0h%2BhZUdY0dOl16O4ExuqVIM0oVk5RxppOZiKRRkYpV8IENA%2B5cR43r9YyitrgO%2FgHvvRBZXQAAAA%3D%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>访问。</p><p>经过一个安静的咒语，湿腿似乎将带着新音乐返回，他们已经稳步取笑了一段时间。在昨晚的演出中，据报道，“躺椅”艺术家在<em>纸浆小说</em>中穿着黑色假发，播放了11首歌曲，其中包括大量的新歌。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">湿腿列表在布莱顿今晚<a href="https://t.co/NDFqMOrpcv">pic.twitter.com/ndfqmorpcv</a></p><p> -  Briony（@briony_may） <a href="https://twitter.com/briony_may/status/1903946641498915101?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年3月23日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wet-leg-announce-their-return-were-so-back-3846997">乐队本周早些时候分享了他们的回归，</a>并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wet-leg-share-teaser-of-first-new-music-in-three-years-3847341">在三年内分享了他们的第一个新材料的30秒预告片，</a>这是新音乐的现场亮相。</p><p>然后，他们宣布了3月31日在布鲁克林市场酒店的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wet-leg-to-kick-off-new-era-with-special-shows-in-new-york-and-la-hey-there-neighbor-3847618">纽约和洛杉矶的两场演出以及4月8日在洛杉矶的河流举行的两场演出的计划</a>。</p><p>他们在Instagram上发表了他们写道：“嘿，邻居有一段时间没有？你为什么不来我们花园的底部？这是我们自己聚会的时候……在纽约市我们和我们的洛杉矶只有几个特殊的夜晚。”</p><p>湿腿邀请球迷于3月28日上市，他们可以<a href="https://laylo.com/wetlegband/m/4Mlj5J" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>注册。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DHjvuvrNWNC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342